Case Study: Effect of Persona Recording Sharing on Automation Team Involvement in Dev Scrum
 
•1. Better Understanding of Sprint Planning
•   - Enables the automation team to grasp task priorities and timelines through access to recorded discussions.
 
•2. Always Up-to-Date with Active Development
•   - Provides real-time updates on development tasks and helps the automation team stay aligned with the dev side.
 
Case Study: Further Enhancements in Automation Team Involvement
 
•3. Early Awareness of Changes Before Rollout
•   - The automation team gets preemptive knowledge of upcoming feature implementations, ensuring automation scripts are prepared ahead of time.
 
•4. Clarification on Discussion Outcomes
•   - Revisit discussions to understand decisions, providing better insights and improving